<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Organize your life here, with the best in technology.">
    <meta name="author" content="EDUDESTROER">
    <title>MakeDay - Become your best!</title>
